The **Events **tab allows to review the list of activities performed by users on the project; for example, the creation of new documents, previews, layout changes, etc.

> Note

*By default, the events of the last 6 months are displayed. It is also possible to download the complete list of events in CSV (comma separated values) format.*

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

For each event, the following information is displayed:

**Information**

**Description**

**Date**

The date and time of the event.

It is possible to apply a filter on the minimum and maximum values.

**Origin**

The origin of the event, i.e. the object type that has been modified (document, family, flow, )

**Name**

The name of the object that has been modified.

**Action**

The action that has triggered the filing of the event.

**Document Family**

The name of the document family that owns the subject of the actions (if applicable).

**Document**

The name of the document that owns the object modified (if applicable).

**User**

The name of the user that performed the action.
